      <equation xml:id="S0.Ex47">
        <MathFork>
          <Math tex="\displaystyle\frac{p}{q}\int_{M}|f^{-}||u|^{q}dv_{g}+\frac{p}{r}\int_{\partial&#10;M%&#10;}|K^{-}||u|^{r}d\sigma_{g}\geq\eta\ell(\int_{M}|f^{-}|dv_{g}+\int_{\partial M}%&#10;|K^{-}|d\sigma_{g})" text="(p / q) * (integral _ M)@(absolute-value@(f ^ -) * (absolute-value@(u)) ^ q * differential-d@(v _ g)) + (p / r) * (integral _ (partial-differential@(M)))@(absolute-value@(K ^ -) * (absolute-value@(u)) ^ r * differential-d@(sigma _ g)) &gt;= eta * ell * ((integral _ M)@(absolute-value@(f ^ -) * differential-d@(v _ g)) + (integral _ (partial-differential@(M)))@(absolute-value@(K ^ -) * differential-d@(sigma _ g)))" xml:id="S0.Ex47.m2">
            <XMath>
              <XMApp>
                <XMTok meaning="greater-than-or-equals" name="geq" role="RELOP">≥</XMTok>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="plus" role="ADDOP">+</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                    <XMApp>

        <MathFork>
          <Math tex="\displaystyle G_{q,r}(u)\geq vol(M)^{1-\frac{p}{q}}a\ell^{\frac{p}{q}}+vol(%&#10;\partial M)^{1-\frac{p}{r}}k\ell^{\frac{p}{r}}+\ell(\eta\int_{M}|f^{-}|dv_{g}+%&#10;\eta\int_{\partial M}|K^{-}|d\sigma_{g})\geq vol(M)^{1-\frac{p}{q}}|a|\ell^{%&#10;\frac{p}{q}}\left[\frac{\eta\int_{M}|f^{-}|dv_{g}}{vol(M)^{1-\frac{p}{q}}|a|}%&#10;\ell^{1-\frac{p}{q}}-1\right]+vol(\partial M)^{1-\frac{p}{r}}|k|\ell^{\frac{p}%&#10;{r}}\left[\frac{\eta\int_{\partial M}|K^{-}|d\sigma_{g}}{vol(\partial M)^{1-%&#10;\frac{p}{r}}|k|}\ell^{1-\frac{p}{r}}-1\right]\geq vol(M)^{1-\frac{p}{q}}|a|%&#10;\ell^{\frac{p}{q}}+vol(\partial M)^{1-\frac{p}{r}}|k|\ell^{\frac{p}{r}}." text="G _ (list@(q, r)) * u &gt;= v * o * l * M ^ (1 - p / q) * a * ell ^ (p / q) + v * o * l * (partial-differential@(M)) ^ (1 - p / r) * k * ell ^ (p / r) + ell * (eta * (integral _ M)@(absolute-value@(f ^ -) * differential-d@(v _ g)) + eta * (integral _ (partial-differential@(M)))@(absolute-value@(K ^ -) * differential-d@(sigma _ g))) &gt;= v * o * l * M ^ (1 - p / q) * absolute-value@(a) * ell ^ (p / q) * delimited-[]@(((eta * (integral _ M)@(absolute-value@(f ^ -) * differential-d@(v _ g))) / (v * o * l * M ^ (1 - p / q) * absolute-value@(a))) * ell ^ (1 - p / q) - 1) + v * o * l * (partial-differential@(M)) ^ (1 - p / r) * absolute-value@(k) * ell ^ (p / r) * delimited-[]@(((eta * (integral _ (partial-differential@(M)))@(absolute-value@(K ^ -) * differential-d@(sigma _ g))) / (v * o * l * (partial-differential@(M)) ^ (1 - p / r) * absolute-value@(k))) * ell ^ (1 - p / r) - 1) &gt;= v * o * l * M ^ (1 - p / q) * absolute-value@(a) * ell ^ (p / q) + v * o * l * (partial-differential@(M)) ^ (1 - p / r) * absolute-value@(k) * ell ^ (p / r)" xml:id="S0.Ex51.m4">

        <MathFork>

    <equation xml:id="S0.Ex107">
      <Math mode="display" tex="\|g(s)\|_{q,M}^{q}+\|g(s)\|_{r,\partial M}^{r}=\frac{\ell_{1}+\ell_{2}}{2}&gt;%&#10;\ell_{1}," text="((norm@(g * s)) _ (list@(q, M))) ^ q + ((norm@(g * s)) _ (list@(r, partial-differential@(M)))) ^ r = (ell _ 1 + ell _ 2) / 2 &gt; ell _ 1" xml:id="S0.Ex107.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex107.m1.7"/>
            <XMWrap>
              <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex107.m1.7">
                <XMTok meaning="multirelation"/>
                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok meaning="plus" role="ADDOP">+</XMTok>
                  <XMApp>
                    <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                    <XMApp>
                      <XMTok role="SUBSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post2"/>
                      <XMDual>
                        <XMApp>
                          <XMTok meaning="norm"/>
                          <XMRef idref="S0.Ex107.m1.7.1"/>
                        </XMApp>
                        <XMWrap>
                          <XMTok meaning="parallel-to" name="||" role="VERTBAR">∥</XMTok>
                          <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex107.m1.7.1">
                            <XMTok meaning="times" role="MULOP">⁢</XMTok>
                            <XMTok font="italic" role="UNKNOWN">g</XMTok>
                            <XMDual>
                              <XMRef idref="S0.Ex107.m1.5"/>
                              <XMWrap>

      <Math mode="display" tex="\ell&lt;\frac{(\sup_{M}f)^{-\frac{n-p}{p}}K_{1}^{-n}}{|\inf_{M}f|+|\inf_{\partial&#10;M%&#10;}K|}," text="ell less (((supremum _ M)@(f)) ^ (- (n - p) / p) * (K _ 1) ^ (- n)) / (absolute-value@((infimum _ M)@(f)) + absolute-value@((infimum _ (partial-differential@(M)))@(K)))" xml:id="S0.Ex113.m1">
        <XMath>
          <XMDual>
            <XMRef idref="S0.Ex113.m1.4"/>

              <XMApp xml:id="S0.Ex113.m1.4">
                <XMTok meaning="less-than" role="RELOP">&lt;</XMTok>

                <XMApp>
                  <XMTok mathstyle="display" meaning="divide" role="FRACOP"/>

                      <XMTok role="SUPERSCRIPTOP" scriptpos="post3"/>
                      <XMDual>
                        <XMRef idref="S0.Ex113.m1.1"/>

                          <XMTok role="OPEN" stretchy="false">(</XMTok>

                        <XMApp>

                          <XMApp>
                            <XMTok fontsize="50%" meaning="minus" role="ADDOP">-</XMTok>

      <Math mode="display" tex="\lim_{(q,r)\to(p^{*},p^{**}}\mu_{q,r}\geq\frac{p}{n}\left[\sup_{M}f\right]^{1-%&#10;\frac{n}{p}}K_{1}^{-n}" text="(limit _ [(q,r)→(p*,p**])@(mu _ (list@(q, r))) &gt;= (p / n) * (delimited-[]@((supremum _ M)@(f))) ^ (1 - n / p) * (K _ 1) ^ (- n)" xml:id="S0.Ex141.m1">
